      "### Scripting vs. Outlining",
      "Creators generally fall into two categories: full scripters who write every word, and outliners who create detailed bullet points and speak naturally around them. AI tools can assist with both approaches. For full scripts, AI generates complete drafts for you to refine. For outlines, AI can expand your bullet points into structured talking points.",
