      "Avoid these common pitfalls when using AI for script writing. Over-reliance on AI without adding personal touches results in generic content. Failing to fact-check AI-generated claims can lead to inaccurate information. Using AI output verbatim without adapting it to your speaking style makes delivery feel unnatural.",
